rComments: He really got a good pace at explaining stuff so that there's enough time for me to comprehend concepts and take notes. He's a really nice and approachable prof! He even went through all our term test papers by himself just to boost our grades.
Professor Jacobson was definitely one of my favourite professors. He really knows his stuff and cares about his students!

Hes a great professor for a very content-heavy-mandatory-for-degree course. Knows his stuff very well and you dont ever doubt that he knows what hes talking about or whether or not hes qualified. He can speak from experiences outside of the university which is sometimes hard to find in the CSI.

One of the nicest profs at this horrid school. Made a point to teach us why the content was important rather than having us memorize largely useless dates. Really wants to see his students succeed. Also, class readings are uploaded.
great professor who really knows history
